--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
2.) Slowers, don't hit the mob with slow during the pull!<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
The best tanks are warriors who can keep aggro (yes there is a taunt key,  yes use the taunt weapons, yes use area taunt!), paladins (&lt;3 stun), SK's once they dont' DOT adds and rangers (&lt;3 &lt;3 snare).<br>
<br>
I will choose a pally or ranger any day over the rest becuase I know I can tash, slow, cripple,weaken and then nuke the shit out of a mob and not even be summoned (talking about teir 3 pop mobs).<br>
<br>
Even with the best warriors I'll still get a summon but what counts is they can pull INSTANT aggro off me if they know what they are doing. Some warriors just don't have what it takes to keep aggro. If a group is formed right an enchanter SHOULD be able to tash/slow/debuff off the bat. <br>
<br>
It's about give and take its' NEVER just the enchanters fault.<br>
<br>
Oh and tell me to wait to slow the trash mobs in elementals which quad for 800. Hahaha ... the WHOLE group either has it or doesn't.<br>
<br>
YOU either SLOW fast or you die ... no playing games. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=383120" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://users.bigpond.net.au/christinaandsimon/EQ/moonlightana.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
