<br>
That seems to be the most difficult thing for me.<br>
<br>
I spent the last 6 to 8 weeks with a beast lord.  And through that time learned when to tash or whatnot, and not be summoned, or if I was summoned, when to do it and not take damage.. we worked well together with the rest of our little group.  Hell we managed to do justice trials on first attempt and aparently thats something hard to do?<br>
<br>
With different classes/players its so hard to know when to tash/slow and when not to.  <br>
<br>
Ive learned that with SK's I can do whatever I want and will never pull agro.<br>
<br>
