<br>
If fighting with an enchanter or necro who is mezzing ... use /assist off!<br>
<br>
The MT may already be looking at the mezzed mob but you don't want to start hitting it as soon as you hit assist.  Wait till the MT hits it THEN assist.<br>
<br>
The enchanter needs a chance to memblur the mezzed mob before mez is broken, otherwise said enchanter will likely be today's lunch.  Mezzed mobs can also be slowed, have resistance lowered, and various other things without breaking mez ... so wait till the enchanter or MT says go.  Autoattack on assist is bad, bad, bad... <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
